Class CacheOutRemover

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.spleen.threading.CacheOutRemover
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class CacheOutRemover
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable
    CacheOutRemover class. MultiThread class that remove automatically the out of date cache objects. Also, remove this objects in order of insertion if the memory space allowed by the configuration is overload.
    Author:
    vallance
